sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AuthenticationService
    participant AuditLog

    User->>AuthenticationService: Request login with credentials
    AuthenticationService->>AuthenticationService: Validate credentials
    AuthenticationService-->>User: Return success or failure

    alt Successful authentication
        AuthenticationService->>AuditLog: Log successful login attempt
        AuditLog-->>AuthenticationService: Confirm log entry
    else Failed authentication
        AuthenticationService->>AuditLog: Log failed login attempt
        AuditLog-->>AuthenticationService: Confirm log entry
    end

    AuthenticationService->>User: Provide access or error message